    "updated_at": "2012-10-07T19:14:28Z",
    "body": "`fn` expressions currently seem to permit `return`, allowing for gross little things [like short-circuiting out of a loop yielding a value](https://gist.github.com/3849236) without declaring a proper, non-anonymous function. Is that use deprecated too?\n",
